org.xtext.project.turn.turn

Interface URNspec

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    URNspecImpl

    public interface URNspec
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'UR Nspec'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Name
    • Info
    • Actors
    • Show As Means End
    • Strat Groups
    • Strategies
    • Ind Conversions
    • Contrib Context Groups
    • Contrib Contexts
    • Ucm Maps
    • Concerns
    • Urnlinks
    • Metadata
    See Also:
    TurnPackage.getURNspec()
